    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001951_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><placeName>Cataracts</placeName> <date when="1863-07-20">20 July
<lb/> 1863</date></dateline><add place="above">132</add>
<lb/>    
<lb/><salute>My Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Meller</persName></salute></opener>

<lb/><p>It has occurred
<lb/>to me since you
<lb/>left that possibly
<lb/>you might like
<lb/>to go at once down
<lb/>to the Kongone<!-- should this word be tagged as something? -->
<lb/>where the <app><rdg cert="medium">Rajind</rdg><rdg>Rajird</rdg></app><!-- should this be tagged? --> is 
<lb/>to touch in August
<lb/>and leave the <placeName><geogName type="region">Cape</geogName></placeName> -
<lb/><unclear cert="low">wait</unclear> of your luggage
<lb/>to go with "Pioneer"</p>
<!-- unsure if he is beginning a new paragraph here --><p><cb rend="vertical"/>Fell Waller I write him after Alwah</p>
	<pb facs="liv_001951_0002" n="0002"/>
<p>
<lb/>as the end of the
<lb/>year - the difficulty
<lb/>of luggage presented
<lb/>my thinking of
<lb/>this before the
<lb/>bishop came up
<lb/> but though we
<lb/>can scarcely ask
<lb/>it - if he <!-- variant reading could or would -->
<lb/>be prevailed on
<lb/>to stop one day
<lb/>more you could
<lb/>give directions to
<lb/>the <term type="occupation">Steward</term> about
	<pb facs="liv_001951_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>the bulkier articles
<lb/>being packed &amp;
<lb/>possibly be favoured
<lb/>with a passage
<lb/>in his boat to
<lb/><unclear cert="medium">Mazaro</unclear> - Hence
<lb/>I write for a
<lb/>canoe to go down
<lb/>to the bar by Kongone
<lb/>for our stores
<lb/>and I could give
<lb/>you some pieces 
<lb/>of cloth to pay
<lb/>your way in
<lb/>the matter <unclear cert="low">of food</unclear>
    <pb facs="liv_00191951_0004" n="0004"/>      
<lb/>the wish of the Gov<hi rend="sup underline">t</hi>
<lb/>that salaries should
<lb/>cease by 31<hi rend="sup">st</hi> Dec<hi rend="sup underline"><unclear cert="medium">r</unclear></hi>
<lb/>makes me mention 
<lb/>this plan though
<lb/>it may not be
<lb/>quite agreeable - I think
<lb/>about it - <persName>Captain
<lb/>Gardner</persName> says the Rajind
<lb/>will call "as the end
<lb/>of August" &amp; I write
<lb/>to the captain to go
<lb/>round &amp; take our
<lb/>late companions off
<lb/>from Liullumane so
<lb/>you might make up to
<lb/>them yet <persName>David Livingstone</persName><!-- unofficial closer -->
</p>
